#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.ldexp.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.ldexp"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp:1 of
msgid "Returns x1 * 2**x2, element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素返回 x1 * 2**x2。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp:3 of
msgid ""
"The mantissas `x1` and twos exponents `x2` are used to construct floating"
" point numbers ``x1 * 2**x2``."
msgstr "使用尾数 `x1` 和以2为底的指数 `x2` 来构造浮点数 ``x1 * 2**x2``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp:6 of
msgid "Tensor of multipliers."
msgstr "乘数张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp:8 of
msgid "Tensor of twos exponents."
msgstr "以2为底的指数张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp:10 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可广播至输入形状。如果未提供或为 "
"`None`，将返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅能作为关键字参数）的长度必须等于"
"输出数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp:15 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "True 值表示在该位置计算 ufunc，False 值表示保留输出中的原值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp:20 of
msgid "**y** -- The result of ``x1 * 2**x2``."
msgstr "**y** -- ``x1 * 2**x2`` 的结果。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp:25 of
msgid ":py:obj:`frexp`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp:26 of
msgid "Return (y1, y2) from ``x = y1 * 2**y2``, inverse to `ldexp`."
msgstr "从 ``x = y1 * 2**y2`` 返回 (y1, y2)，是 `ldexp` 的逆运算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp:29 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp:30 of
msgid "Complex dtypes are not supported, they will raise a TypeError."
msgstr "不支持复数数据类型，将引发 TypeError。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp:32 of
msgid ""
"`ldexp` is useful as the inverse of `frexp`, if used by itself it is more"
" clear to simply use the expression ``x1 * 2**x2``."
msgstr ""
"`ldexp` 可作为 `frexp` 的逆运算使用，若单独使用，直接使用表达式 ``x1 * 2*"
"*x2`` 更为清晰。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.ldexp.ldexp:36 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

